      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_InvoicePaymentRetrieve_EFT_Excel",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve invoice payment details from a view named "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Invoice.vwInvoicePayments",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". It allows filtering by either "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "invoiceId",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " or "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "invoiceNumber",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and formats the results for export, likely to Excel, given the procedure's name. The procedure also logs its execution details, including any exceptions, using another stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "dbo.USP_AppLogCreate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple input parameters, conditional logic, error handling, and logging, which adds to its complexity. However, it primarily performs a straightforward SELECT operation with some data formatting, keeping it from being highly complex."
        }
      ]
    },
